node.text:
Scandinavian Team Battle recap!
Thanks @jakobebskamp, @christianingels & @copenhilldk for organizing the event! 
Shout out to all the riders, especially @emilgranbom representing Team Sweden together with me!
And shout out @donemillange for the tunes 🎵
#ScandinavianTeamBattle 
@gopro @head_freeskiing

node.text:
Dream come true! #unrailisticinvitational 

Thanks @redbullsweden for making this happen!
Also thanks to @gopro @scandinavianshaper @skistar_are @areguiderna @radinnofficial and all the riders 🙏
I’ll post more clips soon!

Finally got to spend some more time on this rail!
Thanks @redbullsweden 🙏
@gopro @scandinavianshaper
🎥: @alexanderryden_film
#unrailisticinvitational
